in the bathroom in the mornings.

23:07.211 --> 23:09.344
Quicker in the bathroom, check.

23:09.388 --> 23:11.694
And, also...

23:11.738 --> 23:13.435
when you come home
later than 9:00,

23:13.479 --> 23:15.959
