unless it's something
that we can sustain long term.

30:10.634 --> 30:12.636
And we can't
sustain this.

30:12.680 --> 30:14.334
I just want to do
everything possible.

30:14.377 --> 30:15.726
Don't we owe him that?

30:15.770 --> 30:17.250
We are.

30:17.293 --> 30:18.817
And we will.

30:18.860 --> 30:21.558
But we also
have to enjoy our son.

30:21.602 --> 30:23.256
And live our lives.

30:26.781 --> 30:28.565
Let's just relax
the food rules

30:28.609 --> 30:30.350
on the weekends.

30:30.393 --> 30:32.569
Let him have cake
at birthday parties.

30:32.613 --> 30:34.920
Yeah.

30:34.963 --> 30:36.660
Okay.

30:36.704 --> 30:38.706
No more
running to school.Oh, thank God.

30:38.749 --> 30:40.969
Mm. Let's throw out
that stupid notebook.

30:41.013 --> 30:42.971
I love the notebook.

30:43.015 --> 30:45.060
Can't we just
keep the notebook?

30:50.457 --> 30:53.242
This is nice out here.

30:53.286 --> 30:55.114
Yeah, I needed this.

30:58.204 --> 31:00.206
So? How'd your date go?

31:03.078 --> 31:05.254
Not bad.
Cool.

31:05.298 --> 31:07.082
What does
"not bad" mean?

31:07.126 --> 31:09.780
That I don't want
to get into it.
Gotcha.
Understood.

31:09.824 --> 31:13.349
I will tell you if
there's something worth telling.

31:13.393 --> 31:15.351
Perfect.

31:16.439 --> 31:17.658
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Aw.

31:17.701 --> 31:21.053
Look at them. So mature.

31:21.096 --> 31:22.619
Less mature...

31:22.663 --> 31:24.099
I'm sorry
for my outburst.

31:24.143 --> 31:27.363
But River Fields is after you.

31:27.407 --> 31:29.148
You have to believe me.

31:29.191 --> 31:31.150
Xiomara, she just got
caught up with the scene.

31:31.193 --> 31:32.586
Please, let this go.

31:34.805 --> 31:36.938
Can we talk?

31:39.810 --> 31:42.204
I want to apologize.

31:42.248 --> 31:44.293
I honestly did not hear

31:44.337 --> 31:45.686
the director call "cut."

31:45.729 --> 31:47.862
But beyond that,

31:47.906 --> 31:50.778
I should never have
kissed your husband.

31:50.821 --> 31:54.738
And even though what I did
is totally unforgivable,

31:54.782 --> 31:56.915
I still wanted
to apologize to you.

31:56.958 --> 31:59.091
Sometimes I get
caught up

31:59.134 --> 32:01.397
in the fantasy.

32:01.441 --> 32:03.573
I lose myself in the role

32:03.617 --> 32:05.532
and...
as pathetic

32:05.575 --> 32:09.884
as it sounds, I start
to believe what I'm feeling.

32:09.928 --> 32:12.669
It's a combination of...
being method

32:12.713 --> 32:15.498
and...
and, well,

32:15.542 --> 32:16.978
being a little lonely,

32:17.022 --> 32:19.676
if I'm...
if I'm being honest.

32:19.720 --> 32:21.678
But it's no excuse.

32:21.722 --> 32:24.203
And nothing like that
will ever happen again.

32:24.246 --> 32:25.726
You have my word.

32:25.769 --> 32:28.947
Okay, then thank you
for saying that.

32:30.731 --> 32:33.429
I'll-I'll get out of your hair.

32:33.473 --> 32:35.257
I'll see you
at home?
Yes.

32:40.871 --> 32:42.047
Thank you for doing that.

32:42.090 --> 32:44.092
No problem.

32:46.921 --> 32:48.662
Oh!

32:48.705 --> 32:49.750
You slapped me?

32:49.793 --> 32:50.881
Uh!

32:50.925 --> 32:52.144
Well, you kissed me!

32:52.187 --> 32:54.755
Because your wife bought
our cover story.

32:54.798 --> 32:55.974
Our what?

32:56.017 --> 32:57.932
There is no cover story.

32:57.976 --> 32:59.281
Let me make this
perfectly clear.

32:59.325 --> 33:00.891
I love my wife.

33:00.935 --> 33:02.241
I don't want
to have sex with you,

33:02.284 --> 33:04.112
I have never wanted
to have sex with you,

33:04.156 --> 33:05.809
and if you keep trying
to have sex with me,

33:05.853 --> 33:07.028
I'm going to HR,

33:07.072 --> 33:08.247
and if they don't
pay attention,

33:08.290 --> 33:10.945
I'll go to Alyssa Milano.

33:17.517 --> 33:19.998
ALBA: Jorge...

33:25.481 --> 33:27.875
Hey. I need a place to stay.

33:27.918 --> 33:30.269
Yeah, sure. Come in.
I just need to make a call.

33:30.312 --> 33:32.053
My last temp screwed up
my injunction,

33:32.097 --> 33:34.055
and now Milos is blocking
the hotel renovation.

33:34.099 --> 33:36.840
Well, maybe that's for the best.

33:36.884 --> 33:38.625
It'll give you time to think
about whether you really

33:38.668 --> 33:40.670
want to go
ahead with it.

33:42.281 --> 33:43.412
Rafael talked to you.

33:43.456 --> 33:45.066
He may have mentioned it,

33:45.110 --> 33:47.286
but that's not
the point. I...

33:47.329 --> 33:48.809
I'm worried that
this renovation

33:48.852 --> 33:51.072
is just one big, old
distraction from J.R.

33:51.116 --> 33:52.595
Yeah, of course it is.

33:52.639 --> 33:53.770
Everywhere I look,
I see reminders of her.

33:53.814 --> 33:54.771
I can't take it.

33:54.815 --> 33:56.469
So you're gonna...

33:56.512 --> 33:58.732
redecorate her
out of your memory?Exactly.

33:58.775 --> 34:00.647
As soon as I get
that injunction.

34:00.690 --> 34:02.040
Judge Judy stayed here
last month with her grandkids.

34:02.083 --> 34:03.171
I'll give her a call.

34:03.215 --> 34:04.868
Eh... It's 11:00 on a weeknight.

34:04.912 --> 34:06.566
You cannot call
Judge Judy right now.

34:06.609 --> 34:08.089
Of course I can!
Give it to me.

34:08.133 --> 34:09.960
Not a chance.
I am your friend,

34:10.004 --> 34:12.006
and I am not giving this phone
back until you agree

34:12.050 --> 34:13.138
to stop
bankrupting yourself

34:13.181 --> 34:15.183
to erase J.R.

34:18.230 --> 34:21.842
It's not just about erasing her.

34:21.885 --> 34:23.148
I want her back.

34:23.191 --> 34:24.975
But I can't have her.

34:25.019 --> 34:27.021
And I feel totally
out of control and powerless,

34:27.065 --> 34:28.849
and I don't know
what to do with myself

34:28.892 --> 34:31.330
and I have to do something
or I'm going to explode.

34:31.373 --> 34:33.549
Get your sneakers.

34:33.593 --> 34:35.290
PETRA:
Why are we doing this again?

34:35.334 --> 34:38.293
When your emotions and
energy levels are too high,

34:38.337 --> 34:39.729
heavy exercise can help.

34:39.773 --> 34:41.818
It's not.
Yeah. Keep running.

34:41.862 --> 34:43.777
I don't know if you've ever been
heartbroken before.

34:43.820 --> 34:44.778
Have you?

34:44.821 --> 34:46.214
Not like this.

34:46.258 --> 34:47.955
Not even close.
I blame you.

34:47.998 --> 34:49.391
Of course you do.

34:49.435 --> 34:50.653
For what, exactly?

34:50.697 --> 34:52.002
Well, I never
believed in

34:52.046 --> 34:53.917
this sappy destiny
stuff before.

34:53.961 --> 34:56.616
And for a while there,
because of you,

34:56.659 --> 34:58.835
I actually thought
J.R. was my...

34:58.879 --> 34:59.923
happily ever after.

34:59.967 --> 35:01.621
Well, if it helps,

35:01.664 --> 35:03.144
I'm over that now.

35:03.188 --> 35:04.145
I thought
Rafael and I

35:04.189 --> 35:05.538
would make it,

35:05.581 --> 35:07.453
but I might change
the end of my book

35:07.496 --> 35:10.412
so the heroine ends up
living with her abuela.

35:10.456 --> 35:11.979
Okay.

35:12.022 --> 35:13.502
That makes no sense.

35:13.546 --> 35:16.070
And I'm done.

35:17.941 --> 35:20.770
Why would the heroine
live with her grandmother?

35:20.814 --> 35:23.860
She's a grown-ass woman.

35:23.904 --> 35:26.036
Can't she move out
even if she doesn't get the guy?

35:27.951 --> 35:29.301
Yeah, I guess she can.

35:29.344 --> 35:31.085
So why hasn't she?

35:32.739 --> 35:33.914
I don't know.

35:33.957 --> 35:35.872
Maybe she was waiting

35:35.916 --> 35:38.875
for things to change.

35:38.919 --> 35:41.095
Is she done waiting?

35:43.924 --> 35:45.882
Yeah, she is.

35:45.926 --> 35:47.928
And is she ready
to not renovate?

35:47.971 --> 35:49.886
No, I'm-I'm not she.
You're she.

35:49.930 --> 35:51.149
Fine, fine.

35:51.192 --> 35:52.150
Are you?

35:53.977 --> 35:56.328
Bankrupting myself
probably isn't the...

35:56.371 --> 35:59.026
healthiest way to get over J.R.

36:11.081 --> 36:12.822
Well, you were right. Uh...

36:12.866 --> 36:14.433
River kissed me again.

36:14.476 --> 36:16.043
I knew it.

36:16.086 --> 36:17.914
I'm sorry.
I told her off--

36:17.958 --> 36:19.612
in no uncertain terms,
this time.

36:19.655 --> 36:21.222
Good!

36:21.266 --> 36:23.572
And you're not allowed to do any
sex scenes with her anymore.

36:23.616 --> 36:25.966
Xiomara, she plays my wife.

36:26.009 --> 36:27.576
Sex scenes are involved.

36:27.620 --> 36:30.144
Then I'm gonna be there,
watching like a hawk.

36:30.188 --> 36:31.189
I told her
to back off.

36:31.232 --> 36:32.277
She got the message this time.

36:32.320 --> 36:33.843
I'm still coming.You can't.

36:33.887 --> 36:35.193
Why not?Because you
being there

36:35.236 --> 36:36.716
will make the situation worse.

36:36.759 --> 36:37.978
Well, it's gonna be worse, then,

36:38.021 --> 36:39.675
because I'll be there.You are not.

36:39.719 --> 36:40.720
I forbid it.

36:40.763 --> 36:42.025
You forbid it?

36:42.069 --> 36:43.636
Oh, excuse me,

36:43.679 --> 36:45.986
I didn't realize
we were back in the cave!

36:46.029 --> 36:48.031
My work pays for this cave.

36:48.075 --> 36:49.729
And I will not let you
jeopardize my job

36:49.772 --> 36:51.513
because you're jealous
and insecure.

36:51.557 --> 36:53.036
Go to hell, Rogelio!

36:53.080 --> 36:54.255
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Uh-oh. Looks like someone's

36:54.299 --> 36:55.343
the man of the doghouse.

37:00.827 --> 37:03.569
Okay, I'm sorry.
Come back.

37:03.612 --> 37:04.570
Xiomara, don't leave!

37:09.227 --> 37:11.533
Wh-What is wrong?
Why are you smiling?

37:11.577 --> 37:15.233
You called me jealous
and insecure.

37:15.276 --> 37:16.973
And it hit me that...

37:17.017 --> 37:18.453
that's true!

37:18.497 --> 37:20.890
I am jealous
and insecure!

37:20.934 --> 37:23.806
And even though
that's a crappy feeling...

37:24.851 --> 37:27.636
...that's a normal feeling.

37:27.680 --> 37:30.639
Normal like before I had cancer.

37:30.683 --> 37:32.902
You're right.

37:32.946 --> 37:35.601
And I yelled at you
for being jealous and insecure!

37:35.644 --> 37:37.037
I know!

37:37.080 --> 37:38.995
You never would have yelled
at me before the PET scan.

37:39.039 --> 37:41.433
Oh...

37:41.476 --> 37:43.391
We're getting back to normal.

37:43.435 --> 37:45.959
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Unlike Rogelio's last kiss,

37:46.002 --> 37:48.918
this is a very wanted advance.

37:48.962 --> 37:50.137
Thank you for yelling at me.

37:50.180 --> 37:52.661
I'm prepared to yell
at you all night long.

37:52.705 --> 37:55.055
And after a five-year
rest period,

37:55.098 --> 37:57.057
I'll be ready to yell
at you some more.

37:57.100 --> 37:59.015
Oh, I plan to yell, too.

37:59.059 --> 38:01.279
And yes, friends,
that's how Xo and Ro

38:01.322 --> 38:03.281
got their groove back.

38:04.543 --> 38:06.719
Not feeling so groovy...

38:20.036 --> 38:21.995
Don't call her, Petra.

38:22.038 --> 38:24.519
You're moving forward,
remember?

38:28.958 --> 38:31.744
P-Please. No...
It's been torture,

38:31.787 --> 38:33.006
not having you here.

38:33.049 --> 38:34.921
Look, I-I... I need you back.

38:34.964 --> 38:37.532
What we have doesn't come around
every day.

38:37.576 --> 38:39.578
So much for
Petra's fresh start.

38:39.621 --> 38:41.362
And you picked up the phone.

38:41.406 --> 38:43.059
Look, you wouldn't
have done that

38:43.103 --> 38:45.410
if a small part of you
didn't miss me, too.

38:46.976 --> 38:49.414
So what will it take
for you to come back to me?

38:49.457 --> 38:51.633
I'd consider it

38:51.677 --> 38:53.156
for triple my salary.

38:53.200 --> 38:55.115
Done.
You're worth every penny.

38:55.158 --> 38:58.336
And way cheaper than renovating the entire hotel.

38:58.379 --> 39:01.034
And I want a lunch hour
every day.

39:01.077 --> 39:02.252
Every day?

39:02.296 --> 39:03.950
Good-bye, Mrs. Solano.

39:03.993 --> 39:04.994
It's a deal.

39:05.038 --> 39:05.995
But you start tomorrow.

39:06.039 --> 39:08.258
See you then.

39:10.391 --> 39:14.003
Well, at least she got
one of her exes back.

39:14.047 --> 39:17.093
And continuing
our apology tour...

39:17.137 --> 39:19.922
And, again,
I'm just so sorry.

39:19.966 --> 39:22.925
It's your life, and I had
no right to criticize it.

39:29.671 --> 39:31.673
Oh, you don't have
to explain anything.

39:59.353 --> 40:01.399
I'm glad.

40:05.141 --> 40:07.143
Yeah, but it's
a good one.

40:07.187 --> 40:09.319
And it made me realize

40:09.363 --> 40:11.713
it's time for a change
for me, too.

40:12.627 --> 40:15.413
So... I'm moving out.

40:17.980 --> 40:19.547
I know.

40:19.591 --> 40:21.419
But what am I waiting for?

40:21.462 --> 40:23.421
Mateo and I will get a studio,

40:23.464 --> 40:25.031
which is what
I can afford right now.

40:25.074 --> 40:26.641
Down the road,
hopefully something bigger.

40:29.949 --> 40:31.603
I don't.

40:31.646 --> 40:33.953
I just think it's time
for the next phase in my life.

40:35.433 --> 40:36.999
GIANT BASS:
For what it's worth,

40:37.043 --> 40:39.175
I totally agree.

40:39.219 --> 40:41.961
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
And speaking of moving forward
with life...

40:42.004 --> 40:45.094
So... last night was nice.

40:45.138 --> 40:47.749
So was this
morning.

40:47.793 --> 40:49.882
It was.

40:51.536 --> 40:54.060
But it didn't exactly solve

40:54.103 --> 40:56.149
all my insecurity
and jealousy.

40:57.803 --> 40:59.021
I know.

40:59.065 --> 41:01.328
And you can come to set
if you want to.

41:01.371 --> 41:03.069
I don't want to.

41:03.112 --> 41:05.027
But that's the thing.

41:05.071 --> 41:07.073
I want to get my own life
back on track.

41:07.116 --> 41:09.684
Figure out what comes next.

41:09.728 --> 41:12.121
And I want to trust you.

41:12.165 --> 41:13.862
I should trust you.

41:13.906 --> 41:16.517
Well, I should have trusted you

41:16.561 --> 41:19.912
when you said you felt like
River didn't get the message.

41:19.955 --> 41:22.044
But I promise you, Xiomara,

41:22.088 --> 41:23.916
she got it this time.

41:23.959 --> 41:27.093
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
True, for the record.

41:27.136 --> 41:30.662
But while Rogelio's home life
might be back to normal...

41:35.580 --> 41:39.366
...his work life is about
to get very uncomfortable.

41:39.409 --> 41:41.411
He loves me not.

41:43.326 --> 41:45.328
He will pay.

41:46.504 --> 41:49.289
He loves me not.

41:49.332 --> 41:50.508
He will pay.

